    <section id="Falcon+Project+Incubation+Status">
      <title>Falcon Project Incubation Status</title>
      <p>This page tracks the project status, incubator-wise. For more general
         project status, look on the project website.</p>
      <p><span class="graduated">The Falcon project graduated on 2014-12-17</span></p>
    </section>
    <section id="Description">
      <title>Description</title>
      <p>Falcon is a data processing and management solution for Hadoop
          designed for data motion, coordination of data pipelines, lifecycle
          management, and data discovery. Falcon enables end consumers to
          quickly onboard their data and its associated processing and
          management tasks on Hadoop clusters.</p>
    </section>
